  "keyFeatures": [
    "Pure Go implementation with no external dependencies",
    "Fluent chainable API for building quantum circuits",
    "Full set of standard quantum gates (H, X, Y, Z, S, T, CNOT, CCNOT, Swap, QFT, etc.)",
    "Arbitrary single-qubit unitary gate U(theta, phi, lambda) and controlled variants",
    "Density matrix formalism for mixed states and open quantum systems",
    "Quantum noise channels: BitFlip, PhaseFlip, Depolarizing, AmplitudeDamping, PhaseDamping",
    "Measurement with probabilistic collapse and state inspection",
    "Built-in implementations of Grover search, Shor factoring, and quantum teleportation",
    "Math utilities: matrix algebra, number-theoretic functions (GCD, modular exponentiation, continued fractions), vectors"
  ],
